{"tid":2462126,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登稱非尋求衝突　向習近平提及美國的自由人權價值觀","createTime":"2021-03-25T22:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T22:20:59.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"149c96aeaae3a6e9e71d68573bc24db9c3639257","tid":2462126,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T22:05:17.000Z","msg":"拜登稱非尋求衝突　向習近平提及美國的自由人權價值觀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582650-20210326.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582650-20210326.htm&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1Gpsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=c1818b90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582650-20210326.htm&h=12dc65d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582650-20210326.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登表示，他明確向國家主席習近平表示，美國並不是尋求衝突。<br />\n<br />\n他在上任後首次記者會上指出，向習近平提及美國對自由及人權的價值觀，形容習近平為人機智，但骨子裡沒有民主。他強調，美國會繼續在新疆維吾爾族人及香港問題上發聲，又聲言要中國對南海、台灣及其他問題負責。<br />\n<br />\n拜登又認為，中國的目標是要領導世界，美國有需要加強投資，與中國競爭。"},{"pid":"cc76a05e83acf20545de6a42b468fb04e8d3f66a","tid":2462126,"uid":244332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T22:10:21.000Z","msg":"sor 笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17cc64817c18de2c5649cd6cebdf4a181c7a2e42","tid":2462126,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T22:16:05.000Z","msg":"到時重記得先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab1e2311d4b26a4e052de3d526dd0a918bf46e7","tid":2462126,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T22:19:39.000Z","msg":"死蠢"},{"pid":"11ba8b756b62c2ef8d0f1952fff4669c6107c1bc","tid":2462126,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T22:20:59.000Z","msg":"人哋同你鬥爭，你就同人競爭，cls"}]}